Package model.users

Class User

java.lang.Object
model.BaseModel
model.users.User
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Copyable, SerializableCopyable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Admin, Doctor, Patient, Pharmacist
public abstract class User extends BaseModel
The base abstract class of a user. Subclasses of User should correspond to the specific users of the application and implement the BaseModel.copy() method.
Since:
2024-10-27
